             was indicted for <rs id="t17831210-10-off63" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17831210-10-off63" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17831210-10-off63" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-10-victim182" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Rogers
                        <interp inst="t17831210-10-victim182" type="surname" value="Rogers"></interp>
