                   in a certain field and open place near the King's highway, on the 1st of November last, and putting him in fear and danger of his, and feloniously taking from his on and against his will, one half crown, value 2 s. 6 d. and one silver sixpence, value 6 d. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17831210-10-victim183" type="victimName">
                        Mary 
